          It looks like a problem of using a wrong generator in CMake
          GUI. I double tested a fresh new downloaded 1.4.3 on my win7
          machine with VS2010, everything worked well.<br>
          <br>
          Please check:<br>
          1.&nbsp; a proper CMake generator is used.<br>
          2.&nbsp; the CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE in CMake GUI and the build type in VS
          are both Release<br>
          <br>
          If the error still happens, please provide me the file name
          and&nbsp; line number where triggers the error when compiling it.<br>
